{"tid":1023922,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"g 嫂 音 樂 台 II 🙄","createTime":"2019-02-16T07:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T12:03:34.000Z","uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"59df4c5d6651eddc5ff5edb8f8715e917e0a65d2","tid":1023922,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:06:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UL3Lbtd7JYo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUL3Lbtd7JYo&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=0722d578\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UL3Lbtd7JYo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lESSuKii0m0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlESSuKii0m0&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=a800a120\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lESSuKii0m0</a><br />\n<br />\n八十年代長髮樂隊除左藍戰士仲有 民間傳奇 同 城市節拍？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d5bf957b7afadd5b66bb5cd8978cffe80463f73","tid":1023922,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:06:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CSvoIsXF2nY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCSvoIsXF2nY&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=a8d91534\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CSvoIsXF2nY</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/409WjHvshkA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F409WjHvshkA&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=9644295c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/409WjHvshkA</a><br />\n<br />\n舊風雲與新風雲？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5aeb49e90806b517fef68ed9dc3305a4584e1f2b","tid":1023922,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_LBgKd5Q0NA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_LBgKd5Q0NA&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=223861ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_LBgKd5Q0NA</a><br />\n<br />\n有頭髮既白花油王子你又見過未 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e572d8a2c9f544ea4e6623bf310338ea20633b01","tid":1023922,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rBnzNGVF-zA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrBnzNGVF-zA&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=bfb8e0e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rBnzNGVF-zA</a><br />\n<br />\n有人話威利「 好大個網」係林振強第一首填詞作品。林燕妮曾經接受訪問，當年林振強寫完俾左黃霑睇，跟住佢就隨手掉入垃圾桶，但最後都灌錄到 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係改編作一首"},{"pid":"36c8b3749be12a9a85a951dd79248837e38e5fac","tid":1023922,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:34:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lexJ2oqrCWk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlexJ2oqrCWk&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=a8003c30\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lexJ2oqrCWk</a><br />\n<br />\nhit得一時既精選雜錦？ <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a54d799cc3c336155321a83c79bfb9cf5cf6baf","tid":1023922,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:47:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C9zDwV1nVqI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC9zDwV1nVqI&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=c46c4abb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C9zDwV1nVqI</a><br />\n<br />\n最近又諗起依首，雖然貼過，遺作亦係好作 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa30bbd5c3345d50a09f2e14f29fa202e41ebdb7","tid":1023922,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:17:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mgzohWAVxNA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmgzohWAVxNA&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=f72663df\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mgzohWAVxNA</a><br />\n<br />\n未光頭既後生仔張衛健 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae0c2b46826e43895bc1f53e5510a93c83e9b230","tid":1023922,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:20:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rDk_-cEkOd0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrDk_-cEkOd0&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=ecd2da36\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rDk_-cEkOd0</a><br />\n<br />\n滾石旗下台灣女歌手中，最投入發展香港市場者，出過三張粵語專輯（不含精選）。蘇慧倫在94年推出首張粵語專輯《我有時會想》，其中〈我一個人住〉的粵語版〈我不是一個人住〉在電台有不錯的播放率。96年推出了《自然喜歡你》和《話說蘇慧倫X檔案》兩張粵語專輯，後者大多數是全新創作歌曲，更請來迪士尼配樂師王宗賢製作和編曲，同時還收錄了〈Lemon Tree〉的粵語版和〈鴨子〉的粵語版〈話說〉。"},{"pid":"73793702d40186ee3b09721c29dd879cf78372c3","tid":1023922,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T15:56:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/noIoeg6yN9w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnoIoeg6yN9w&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=f5665b8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/noIoeg6yN9w</a><br />\n<br />\n「川鳴」由潘健康、梁兆輝及顏福偉三人組成。那張EP碟，三首作品全由潘健康作曲。<br />\n<br />\n這是林夕最早發表的10首作品之一，他幫Raidas第一張EP寫了《吸煙的女人》、《不願置評》、《杯中冷巷》，同年也為川鳴包辦EP三首詞，除了《午夜場》，還有《孩子 (給被遺棄的一群)》和《歲月》，探討童年、青年、老年三個人生階段，唱片收益捐贈保良局基金，福有攸歸。<br />\n<br />\n川鳴風格接近達明一派，夜渡英倫電子，原曲只有3分17秒之短，remix版延長一分鐘。"},{"pid":"424b4f286b8550eba99446b30923bb522523188b","tid":1023922,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T16:56:19.000Z","msg":"仲未見薑汁兄既，這個老餅音樂台只有我們入 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3eebd126a8ae82d4131c9fed2a8f446de0f483c7","tid":1023922,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:16:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GVgpd5zuEgk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGVgpd5zuEgk&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=542d0503\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GVgpd5zuEgk</a><br />\n<br />\nFace to Face在1990年出道。與&nbsp;Echo（另一隊同期二人女子組合）一樣是注重形象包裝，歌曲路線兩者也大致相近。但 Face to Face 的歌格調較柔和，音樂類型也多樣化，因此也頗受歡迎。以《一些》、《蝶夢》和《情迷Milano》較為熟悉。<br />\n<br />\n1992年，成員吳少芳（Jodi）和其經理人駕車返回將軍澳寓所，在距離寓所還有3分鐘車程的地方與一架泥頭車相撞。這次撞車令吳少芳四肢癱瘓，其經理人亦逝世，蔡慧玲在事故後宣佈退出，Face to Face亦隨之解散。"},{"pid":"9fdceeb138756137ab9452e2cf6dcec98b89148b","tid":1023922,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:24:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QtszAra102I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQtszAra102I&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=f26c666b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QtszAra102I</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/frZaRgExkmE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfrZaRgExkmE&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=e0684d20\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/frZaRgExkmE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6WQa6fCQGkM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6WQa6fCQGkM&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=49428337\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6WQa6fCQGkM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一群志同道合的朋友，興之所至聚在一起自行製作的歌曲專輯，同年 1988 銀星出品 《大話西遊》也是他們最後有參與的，其後因各有各的原工作，各人在各行各業發展，甚至移民，所以《友誼接觸 Friends Connection》也是他們唯一的專輯，也就是說 CD 應不可能推出了。"},{"pid":"5e6fe63508a4a4d478926aac38acd0a3ba5c9b8f","tid":1023922,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:59:45.000Z","msg":"腳趾拍拖了？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3635b52e8dd21cbd1bf6752ef1cb9defe76e7cce","tid":1023922,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腳趾拍拖了？&lt;&gt;</blockquote><br />\n未喎，有都唔會成日上黎 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d25cd11c774fe70ac4