ps://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07e398280c871af0f7b405c0143a409981038123","tid":1023922,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3eebd126a8ae82d4131c9fed2a8f446de0f483c7","tid":1023922,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:16:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GVgpd5zuEgk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGVgpd5zuEgk&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=542d0503\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GVgpd5zuEgk</a><br />\n<br />\nFace to Face在1990年出道。與&nbsp;Echo（另一隊同期二人女子組合）一樣是注重形象包裝，歌曲路線兩者也大致相近。但 Face to Face 的歌格調較柔和，音樂類型也多樣化，因此也頗受歡迎。以《一些》、《蝶夢》和《情迷Milano》較為熟悉。<br />\n<br />\n1992年，成員吳少芳（Jodi）和其經理人駕車返回將軍澳寓所，在距離寓所還有3分鐘車程的地方與一架泥頭車相撞。這次撞車令吳少芳四肢癱瘓，其經理人亦逝世，蔡慧玲在事故後宣佈退出，Face to Face亦隨之解散。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:03:34.000Z","msg":"一些、情迷Milano 好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}